, "comments": 0, "score_up": 16, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZD2OpOO", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 23, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8536004, "raw_content": "\n---\n\n## **Timeline of Attacks by  Iran  Against The United States **\n\n---\n\n### **Nov 4, 1979 \u2013 Jan 20, 1981**\n\n**Event:** Iran Hostage Crisis (Tehran Embassy Seizure)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 66 Americans taken hostage (52 held for 444 days)\n* 17 Americans killed (63 total deaths related)\n\n---\n\n### **Apr 1983**\n\n**Event:** U.S. Embassy Bombing (Beirut)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 63 killed (17 Americans)\n\n---\n\n### **Oct 1983**\n\n**Event:** Marine Barracks Bombing (Beirut)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 241 U.S. personnel killed\n\n---\n\n### **Dec 1983**\n\n**Event:** Bombing at U.S. Embassy (Kuwait City)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* No Americans killed\n\n---\n\n### **Mar 1984 (Killed in 1985)**\n\n**Event:** Kidnapping of CIA Station Chief William Buckley (Beirut)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* Tortured and killed (1985)\n\n---\n\n### **Dec 1984**\n\n**Event:** U.S. Embassy Annex Bombing (Beirut)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 2 U.S. officials killed\n\n---\n\n### **Jun 1985**\n\n**Event:** Hijacking of TWA Flight 847\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 1 U.S. Navy diver killed\n\n---\n\n### **Jul 1989**\n\n**Event:** Execution of U.S. Marine Col. William Higgins (Lebanon)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 1 American killed\n\n---\n\n### **Jun 1996**\n\n**Event:** Khobar Towers Bombing (Saudi Arabia)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 19 Americans killed\n* ~500 injured\n\n---\n\n### **2003 \u2013 2011**\n\n**Event:** Attacks in Iraq\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* At least 603 U.S. troops killed\n\n---\n\n### **Jan 2007**\n\n**Event:** Karbala Attack (Iraq)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 5 U.S. soldiers killed\n\n---\n\n### **Dec 2019**\n\n**Event:** Rocket Attack on K1 Base (Kirkuk, Iraq)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 1 U.S. contractor killed\n\n---\n\n### **Jan 2020**\n\n**Event:** Ballistic Missile Attack on Ain al-Asad Base (Iraq)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* Over 100 U.S. troops injured\n\n---\n\n### **Feb 2021**\n\n**Event:** Rocket Attack (Iraq)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 1 U.S. service member killed\n* 4 contractors wounded\n\n---\n\n### **Jul 2021**\n\n**Event:** Additional Attacks (Iraq/Syria)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 2 U.S. service members wounded\n\n---\n\n### **Sep 2022**\n\n**Event:** Attack in Iraq/Syria region\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 1 American killed\n\n---\n\n### **Mar 2023**\n\n**Event:** Drone Strike near Hasakah (Syria)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* 1 U.S. contractor killed\n* 5 service members + 1 contractor wounded\n\n---\n\n### **Oct 7, 2023**\n\n**Event:** Attack in Southern Israel\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* At least 48 Americans killed\n* 12 Americans kidnapped\n\n---\n\n### **Late 2023 (Oct\u2013Dec)**\n\n**Event:** Series of Drone/Rocket Attacks (Iraq, Syria, Jordan)\n**Details / Casualties (U.S.):**\n\n* Over 180 attacks on U.S. forces in the Middle East\n\n---\n\n", "author": "Trumptrumptrumpp", "created": 1775325986669, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Han_Schlomo", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Timeline of Attacks by  Iran  Against The United States ", "last_comment_created": 1775331930479, "content": "<hr />\n<h2>**Timeline of Attacks by  Iran  Against The United States **</h2>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Nov 4, 1979 \u2013 Jan 20, 1981</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Iran Hostage Crisis (Tehran Embassy Seizure)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>66 Americans taken hostage (52 held for 444 days)</li>\n<li>17 Americans killed (63 total deaths related)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Apr 1983</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> U.S. Embassy Bombing (Beirut)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>63 killed (17 Americans)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Oct 1983</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Marine Barracks Bombing (Beirut)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>241 U.S. personnel killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Dec 1983</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Bombing at U.S. Embassy (Kuwait City)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>No Americans killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Mar 1984 (Killed in 1985)</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Kidnapping of CIA Station Chief William Buckley (Beirut)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tortured and killed (1985)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Dec 1984</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> U.S. Embassy Annex Bombing (Beirut)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>2 U.S. officials killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Jun 1985</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Hijacking of TWA Flight 847\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 U.S. Navy diver killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Jul 1989</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Execution of U.S. Marine Col. William Higgins (Lebanon)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 American killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Jun 1996</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Khobar Towers Bombing (Saudi Arabia)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>19 Americans killed</li>\n<li>~500 injured</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>2003 \u2013 2011</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Attacks in Iraq\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>At least 603 U.S. troops killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Jan 2007</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Karbala Attack (Iraq)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>5 U.S. soldiers killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Dec 2019</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Rocket Attack on K1 Base (Kirkuk, Iraq)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 U.S. contractor killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Jan 2020</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Ballistic Missile Attack on Ain al-Asad Base (Iraq)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Over 100 U.S. troops injured</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Feb 2021</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Rocket Attack (Iraq)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 U.S. service member killed</li>\n<li>4 contractors wounded</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Jul 2021</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Additional Attacks (Iraq/Syria)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>2 U.S. service members wounded</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Sep 2022</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Attack in Iraq/Syria region\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 American killed</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Mar 2023</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Drone Strike near Hasakah (Syria)\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 U.S. contractor killed</li>\n<li>5 service members + 1 contractor wounded</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Oct 7, 2023</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Event:</strong> Attack in Southern Israel\n<strong>Details / Casualties (U.S.):</strong></p>\n<ul>\